CLEARNING Null values¶

In [12]:
NFT_df['Floor_Price']=NFT_df['Floor_Price'].replace(np.nan,NFT_df['Floor_Price'].mean())
NFT_df['Floor_Price_USD']=NFT_df['Floor_Price_USD'].replace(np.nan,NFT_df['Floor_Price_USD'].mean())
NFT_df['Owner_Asset_Ratio']=NFT_df['Owner_Asset_Ratio'].replace(np.nan,NFT_df['Owner_Asset_Ratio'].mean())
